                    <msContents>
                        <summary>Book of Greetings Varia: Ff. i v(erso)-iii r(ecto): Calendar of the
                            feast days of the Saints. Collection of Greetings to all of the Godhead,
                            to the Saints and the angels, for hourly chants during Holy Week. Varia:
                            Ff. 80v-84v: Asmat prayer against Shotalay, demon of infant mortality,
                            written in a 20th century hand. Ff. 85r-86r: Asmat prayer for protection
                            from stick (በትር፡), written in hand of the 20th century</summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <textLang/>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
